\id 1TI -Kamano-Kafe
\h 1 Timoti
\toc1 1 Timoti Poli'a Timoti Ese Avonkremi'nea Naneke
\toc2 1 Timoti
\mt1 1 Timoti
\mt2 Poli'a Timoti Ese Avonkremi'nea Naneke
\c 1
\s1 Timoti'ma agra'ama kegava hania zamofo naneke
\p 
\v 1 Hagi nagra Poli'na, Krais Jisasi eri'za ne'mo'na Anumza Tazahu ne'ene Krais Jisasike humanantenate, emema tavaresigu Rantimofo avega nentoa aposolo ne'mo'na,
\v 2 Timotiga nagri tamage mofavremoka mago tamentinti nehu'mokarega, Anumza Nerafantegati'ene Krais Jisasi Ranti'mo'a asunku huganteno asurgi'zane, arimpa fruzana kamisigeno kagrane mesie.
\s1 Havige mono hunezmiza vaheku kva hanaza naneke
\p 
\v 3 Hagi Masedonia katre'na vunaku nehu'na, nagra tutu hugante'noe. Efesasi mani'nenka havi mono huku hanaza nagara, anara osiho hunka nezmasminka,
\v 4 havige hanaza kegu antahi zamige, korapa fore hu'nesia kanihe kerera antahi ozamiho. Na'ankure ana zamo'a hafra fore huno tamaza osina, Anumza'mofontegati erinaku tamentinti hanaza zana e'origahaze.
\v 5 Hianagi tagrama rempi hunezamuna zamofo agafa'a, zamesi nezmante'za zamagu'areti agru hu'ne'za, knare zamagu'zamagesareti zamentinti hugahaze.
\v 6 Na'ankure mago'a rempi huzmi vahe'mo'za knare'zana agatere'za hazagre'za nevu'za, zamaza osugazanku havi naneke nehantagaze.
\v 7 Kasege huzamasmi vahe nesampra'zanagi, zamagra ana kema hazankea antahinira osu'ne'za, antahi'none nehu'za zamufa eri mareri'zageno kemo'a nena'a nomane.
\p 
\v 8 Hu'neanagi tagra antahi'none, kasegemo'a knare hu'negeta, ana kasegema Anumzamo hu'nere, amage anteta avariri sunkeno'a knare hugahie.
\v 9 Hagi tagranena antahi'none kasegema tami'neana fatgozama nehaza vahe'mokizmigure huno ozami'ne. Hagi kasegema ovariri'za ha'nentake nehu'za, Anumzamofo avu'ava nosu'za kumi' nehaza vahe'ene mani otage osu'za, otage huno mani'zanku huhavi'za nehu'za, nezmafano nezamrerano zamahe nefri'za, vahe zamahe nefri'za,
\v 10 monko'za nehaza vahe'ene, vemo vene mase'zane, vahe kumzafa nesea vahe'ene, agi'ari vahe'ene, hu'nesia zanteku vahane hu' vahe'ene, knare'za rempi huzmi zanku huhaviza hu vahe zami'ne.
\v 11 Masanentake konarari'ane Knare Musenke'afi (gospol) asomu'ane Anumzamo'a huzamasmio huno nagrira huhamprinante'nea kante ante'na nezamasmue.
\p 
\v 12 Hagi Krais Jisasi'a tagri Ramo, hihamu nami'negu muse hunentoe. Na'ankure Agra nagri antahinamiteno, erizani'a erigahane huno huhamprinante'ne.
\v 13 Hianagi korapara Anumzamofona nagra azanva ke nehu'na, amage' nentaza vahera zamazeri kore nehu'na, tusiza hu'na Jisasi agifi amage'nentaza vahera harezmante'noe. Ana hu'noanagi asunku hunante'ne. Na'ankure antahi'na ke'na osu'nena namentintia osu'nogu anara hu'noe.
\v 14 Krais Jisasi'a Rantimo asunku hunanteno naza higena Agrite namentinti nehu'na avesinte'noe.
\v 15 Ama'i tamage nanekegino, hakare'a vahe'mo'za zamentinti hugahaze. Na'ankure Krais Jisasi'a kefoza nehaza vahe zamahokehesigu ama mopafina erami'ne. Ana agu'afina nagra zamagtere'na hakare vahera kefo'zana hu'noe.
\v 16 Ana hu'noanagi, nagriku esera asuntagi nante'ne, nagrite vahe'mo'za avame zana nege'za, Agrite kumi' vahe'mo'za esnagu agazone huno zamega anteno mani'ne, Krais Jisasinte zamagra zamentinti nehu'za, kasefa hu'za mani vavahu nomani'zana erigahaze.
\v 17 Menine maka knafima manivava nehia Kini nera, ofrino, vahe'mo onke, magoke Anumzana, konariri'ane manivava hugahie. Tamage.
\p 
\v 18 Hagi magoke tamentinti nehu'a mofavre Timotiga, ama avompima kre negamua nanekegu, kagesa antahio. Ko'ma mago'mofoma Anumzamofo naneke asamigeno, kagriku huama hu'nea kasnampa kefi hankavetinka Rantimofo ha'pina, knare hunka hara huo.
\v 19 Kamentintia azeri hanavetinenka, kagu kagesareti knare antahintahi huo. Na'ankure mago'a vahe'mo'za ana nanekegura zamenosige'za zamentintifina atre'za ventemo tagana vaziankna nehaze.
\v 20 Ana agu'afina Haimenasi ene Aleksandake, e'inahu avamera hu'na'e. Ananku hu'na Sata azampi zanante'noe, Sata'a kna nezanaminke'ne rempi huteke, Anumzamofo agi'amofona azanva kea huontesa'e hu'na hu'noe.
\c 2
\s1 Maka veaku nunamu huzmantesuna naneke
\p 
\v 1 Anumzamofo agihanta vazi'zana pusaza me'ne. Nunamu huta agihanta nevazita, tagri'ma tavesinia zanku antahinegeta, muse hunenteta, maka vahe zamagi erita zamaza hanigu antahigesanune.
\v 2 Kini vaheku'ene maka kva krinerantaza vaheku'ene nunamuna huzmantesune, ana nehanunke'za kva huso'e nehanageta, agazone huta fruzampi Anumzamofo avu'avate'ene fatgo mani'zampi so'e huta magokepi manigahune.
\v 3 E'inahu zamo'a Anumzana Tazahu ne'mofo (Savior) avufina knare nehigeno musena nehie.
\v 4 Kefo zampinti tahoke he'nea ne'mo'a, maka vahe'mo'za tamage naneke antahi'za zamasimu erisazegu ave'nesie.
\v 5 Na'ankure Anumzana magoke mani'ne. Anumzane, vahe'mota amu'nompina, anazanke huno amu'no nera magoke mani'ne, ana nera Krais Jisasi'e.
\v 6 Tusi'a mizanteti Agra'a avufga atreteno, maka veara miza seranteno, Anumzamo'ma huhampri ante'nea kna eri ama hu'ne.
\v 7 Ana zanteku huno nagrira nazeri oti'ne, Anumzamofo mono naneke zamasmi'nena antahisnagu, nazeri oti'nea aposolo ne'mo'na, nagra tamage nehuanki havigea nosue. Zamufaga taga osu vahe (gentiles) rempi huzminena zamentinti hu'za tamage nanekea antahihogu huama nehue.
\p 
\v 8 E'ina hu'negu nagri'ma nave'nesiana hakare'a kumate vene'nemo'za, ruotage zamazana antesga hu'za nunamuna nehu'za, fra vazi'za ke hakare osiho.
\s1 A'nemo'za zamavuzmavama hanaza zamofo naneke
\p 
\v 9 Hagi nagri'ma navesiana, a'nemo'za fatgo huza kukena nehu'za, zamavasesema hanafina vahe'mo'za kezmasane hu'zana nosuza, zamanu zamazoka hane'zane, golire trohunte'naza avasase zane, hage rimpinti zane (pearl), marerisa kukena osiho.
\v 10 Hu'neanagi Anumzamofo amage' nentonema hanaza a'nemo'za, knare avu'ava nehu'za, ana avu'avateti knare avasese hiaza hu'za hugahaze.
\v 11 A'mo'a akohe'no rempi humisia ke erizafa nehuno, ke amage' anteno, agazone huno manigahie.
\v 12 Hu'neanagi nagra a'nemo'za vene'nea rempi huzmi zankuro, kva mani'zankura navenosie. E'igu agazone hu'za manisanaze.
\v 13 Na'ankure koteno ve Adamu tro huteno, henka'a ara, Ivina tro hu'ne.
\v 14 Adamuntera revatga zana fore osu'ne, hagi a'mofo revatga higeno, kumi'pina traka hu'ne.
\v 15 Hu'neanagi a'nemo'za mofavrema kase nezmante'za, zamentinti nehu'za, ovesinte avesinte nehu'za, mani ruotage hu'za nemani'za, zamagu'ane zamagi'ene, kva hanaza zamo knare mani'zana erigahaze.
\c 3
\s1 Mono nonte kva hanaza vahe'ene Dikeni vahe'mofo naneke
\p 
\v 1 Hagi ama'i tamage naneke, iza'o mono kva manigahue hanimo'a, knare eri'zane huno erino.
\v 2 Kvama hania ne'mo'a amanahu hino, hazenke'a omneno, magoke a' anteno, mani'zama'a kva nehuno, fatgo zanke nehuno, avufa antermino nemanino, nantu antentesia vahe agampu nehuno, agra knare'za rempi huzmi ne' nemanino,
\v 3 hanave rina neno negi oneno, hafra osuno, hagi arimpa fru nehuno, ke hakare osuno, zagogu avesinte'zana atreno.
\v 4 Agra knare huno naga'a kva nehuno, mofavre zaga'a zamazeri fatgo hanige'za, knare kante maniho.
\v 5 Hu'neanagi naga'a kvagri so'e nosnimo'a, ina kna huno Anumzamofo mono' nona kegava hugahie?
\v 6 Menima agu'a rukrahe hu'nesnia nera, mono kva ne' manisnie hunka ame'ama hunka azeri o'otio. Agra avufa erisaga nehnigeno Sata'a ana hanifi efreno azeri traka hugahie.
\v 7 Hagi monopi omani megi'a vahe'mo'za nege'za, knare nere nehanageno, agra havi avu'avapina uramino Sata krifufina ohegahie.
\p 
\v 8 Dikenima manisia ne'mo'a, anahu kna huno avu'avapina fatgo huno mani'neno, tare agerura oruno, hanave tintera osuno, havi kantetira vahe'mofo zagoa e'orino,
\v 9 e'inara osuno ani' agu'agesare mani'neno, Anumzamofonte hanave amentintima hu'neana, azeri hampo'na hino.
\v 10 Ana eri'zana erigahazanki hu'nenka, esera avame antenka eri'za zamige'za knare hu'zama erisagenka, dikeni eri'zana zamige'za eriho.
\p 
\v 11 A'nezamimo'zanena anahu kna hu'za knare hu'za nemani'za, vahe zamefi'a ke osu'za, knare avu'ava hu'za fatgo zanke hakareza hanafina nehnage'za antahi zamigahaze.
\v 12 Dikenima manisimo'a magoke a' anteno, mofavre naga'a knare huno kegava negrino, noma'afi zantamine, vahe enena kegava krigahie.
\v 13 Ana dikeni eri'zama knare hu'za erisamo'za knare zamagi eneri'za, eri'za zamifina otine'za, korera osu'za Krais Jisasintera hanaveti'za zamentinti hugahaze.
\p 
\v 14 Nagra ama avoma kre atrogeno kagritega viana, zaza kna omaninesake'na ko e'naku nehue.
\v 15 Hianagi mago'a zamo'ma nazerinke'na omesugenka, nagrama avoma kre troana kagra kenka antahinka hu'nane, vahe'mo'za inankna hu'za Anumzamofo nagara zamagra kegava hugahaze, kasefa huno mani'nea Anumzamofo mono nonte'ma, atru re'nea anumza zafa, tamage kemofo agafa'e.
\v 16 Maka vahe'mota mago trimpa nehune, Anumzamofo avu'avapi tamentintima hu'zamo'a eama nehie, \bdit Kraisi'a avufa erino eama higeno, Avamu'mo fatgo avu'ava'a eriama higeno, ankero'moza kageno, Kraisi agi agenke hakare kaziga huama hazageno, miko mopane mopane vahe'mo'za zamentinti hazageno, tusi'a masanentake konariri'afi avreno mareri'ne.\bdit*
\c 4
\s1 Havigema nehaza vahe'mokizmi naneke
\p 
\v 1 Hu'neanagi Ruotge Avamumo huama huno nerasmie, mago'a kna esnia knafina mago'amo'za zamentintia atre'za evunerami'za, rezmatagahu avamu'ene, hankro'mofo\f + \fr 4:1 \ft Hankrorema hu'neana havi avamuku hu'ne. \f* naneke rempi huzamisage'za zamagesa anteza antahigahaze.
\v 2 Havige vahe'mo'za zamagra hu'za, amanahu vahe mani'none nehaza vahe'mo'za havi kereti rezmatga nehu'za, knare zamagu zamagesa zamagu'afi me'neana, havi kereti zamagu'a kre hagege nehaze.
\v 3 Ana vahe'mo'za arave osugahaze nehu'za, mago'a kavera oneho hanazanagi, tamage ke'arema tamentinti nehutma nentahimota Anumzamo'ma tro hunte'nea zana muse hunenteta susu huta erigahaze.
\v 4 Na'ankure hakare'zama Anumzamo'ma tro hunte'nea zamo'a, knare hu'negu mago'zana otreta tamagra susu hunentetma amne erigahaze.
\v 5 Na'ankure Anumzamofo ke'mo'ene, nunamumo azeri agru hu'ne.
\s1 Timoti'ma knare eri'za ne' manisia naneke
\p 
\v 6 Hagi ama nanekea hanavetinka monopi mani'naza kafuhe'ima zamasamisunka, kagra knare hunka Krais Jisasi eri'za ne' nemaninka, hanavetinka hakare zupa kamentintifina nehagenka maka knare antahi'zana erinka amage'ma ante'zampina hagegahane.
\v 7 Hu'neanagi kagra maninka tavava'nemofo knihe kerera fra ovazio, hagi kagra knaka'ane, hanaveka'a Anumzamofo avu'avapi kazeri hanavetio.
\v 8 Hanki amega tavufga azeri hanaveti hanuna zamo'a, osi'a knafi taza hu'zana eri gahunanagi, Anumzamofo avu'ava'ma (godliness) hanuna zana huvempa hu'negu meni mani'zampina taza nehuno, henkama esia mani'zampinena taza hugahie.
\v 9 Ama nanekea tamage naneke me'negu antahi hanavetita erisnune.
\v 10 Amana zante amuho huta eri'zana enerita maraguzanetune, na'ankure kasefa huno mani'nea Anumzamo'ma esanigu tagra tamentinti nehune. Agra mika zamentinti nehaza vahe zamagu'vazino zamahokehe nere. (Savior)
\p 
\v 11 Menima negasamua kea hu ankerenka huzamige'za amage anteho.
\v 12 Atregeno mago vahe'mo'a nehaza ne' mani'nane huno kagehenkamu otreno, hianagi zamentintima nehaza nagatera avame zankna hunka keka'afine, kavukvapine, zamesi zamante zane, kamentintifine, agru hu'zane, huzmeri hugahane.
\v 13 Nagra egahuanki, hakare vahera zamazeri atru hunka avontafera hamprinka mono nanekea huama hunka rempi huzamio.
\v 14 Kagra kagera okanitfa huo, Anumza naneke huama (profesi) hazagenka anampinti Avamu'mofo muse'za (gift) erinke'za, mono kva vahe'mo'za zamaza ante'za eri'za eriogu huhampri kante'naze.
\v 15 Mika zupa kagra ama erizana kegava nehunka, anampinka eri'zana enerisankeno nena'a fore hanige'za vahe'mo'za kegahaze.
\v 16 Kagrama kavukvama nehanazana kegava negrinka, rempima vahe'ma hunezmina kenena kegava nehunka, maka zupa ana zanke hunka nevanankeno'a, Anumzamo kagrira kagunevazino, keka'a antahinamokizmia zamagu'vazigahie.
\c 5
\s1 Kento a'nemofo naneke
\p 
\v 1 Hagi ranra vahekura rankea huontenka, negafanku'ma nehanaza hunka fru kefinti antahigo. Hanki kahefa vahera negafuma huntenaku nehanaza hunka azeri so'e nehunka,
\v 2 ranra a'nea negrerama hunentana kna hunentenka, zahufa a'nea, negasaroma hunentanankna hunka knare antahintahifi fatgo kazigati kva huzmanto.
\p 
\v 3 Mago kva krintega vahe'ma omani'nesia kento a'nea, kva krizamanteho.
\v 4 Hu'neanagi mago kento a'ma mofavre'afi, negehoma maninesuno'a esera zamagra rempi hu'za mono'mo hu'nea kante nozamifi zamarera zamafaza kva krizmante'naza nona hu'za kva huzmanteho, Anumzamofona e'inahu zanku ave'nesie.
\v 5 Ana hianagi agraku nemanisia kento a'mo, Anumzante amentinti nehuno hanine zagene nunamuna huno Anumzana antahigegahie.
\v 6 Hu'neanagi mago kento a'mo agri'ma avenesia zankuke agesa nentahimo'a, kahefa mani'neanagi avamupina ko fri'ne.
\v 7 Vahe'tmina ama naneke zamasmige'za avaririho, e'ina hananke'za mago'amo'za ke huzmante kanku hakegahaze.
\v 8 Hianagi mago'mo'ma kora fatgoama zamazeri so'e osuno, naga'anema zamazeri so'e osnimo'a, amentintimo'a amne zankna hanigeno, zamentinti nosnaza vahera zamagatereno haviza hugahie.
\p 
\v 9 Hanki kento a'nea zamazama hunaku zamagima kresafina 60'a zage kafuma huno, nevente mani fatgo hu'nesia kento a' aza hugahaze.
\v 10 Ana kentomo knare avu'ava nehiaza negesageno, mofavre zaga'a negrino, aru vahe agampu nehuno, mono kva vahe zamaga sese nehuno, knafi mani'nesaza vahe zamaza nehuno, ana eri'zama'a arimpa amino knare huno erigahie.
\v 11 Hu'neanagi kahefa kento a'nea zamaza hunaku zamagima kresafina onkreho, na'ankure zamesi'zamo zamavazu hanige'za Kraisimpi hanaveti'za nemaniza'za atre'za ve erigahaze.
\v 12 Ko'ma huvempa hu'naza kea anama hazazamo rufutagige'za, kea eri'za zamagra'a zamufafi emenentaze.
\v 13 Hagi eri'za e'ori amne mani'neza, ru nompi ru nompi mareritere nehu'za, nosuna naneke nehu'za, rumofo nanekere zamefiga'a ke hu'za vano nehu'za, osuga naneke nehaze.
\v 14 Nagrama nagesa nentahuana, kahefa kento a'nemo'za ve eri'za mofavre nente'za, nozamia kegava nehanage'za, huhavi'za huzmanteku hanaza vahe'mo'za kegura hakregahaze.
\v 15 Na'ankure mago'amo'za hago kana atre'za Sata nevaririze.
\v 16 Hagi mago amentinti nehania a'mo naga'afi kento a'nema mani'nesazana, agra knare'za huno ana a'neramina zamaza hanigeno'a, mono vahera kna eri ozamisageno, zamagra'zmi zamaza huga osune'naza kento a'nea, mono vahe'mo'za zamaza hugahaze.
\s1 Elda kva vahe'mokizmi naneke
\p 
\v 17 Hagi elda vahera, Anumzamofo eri'zante kvagri so'e nehaza vaheki, zamagi erisaga nehuta antegna huta mago'ene zamiho. E'ima hanaveti'za mono ke nehu'za, rempima hunezmi'za vahera mono naga'mo'za zamaza hugahaze.
\v 18 E'i ana kante mono avontafe'mo'a amanage hu'ne, \bdit Bulimakaomo'ma witi raga refuzafupeno anoma'a neharesigeta, zamagitera nofira ana'okiho. \bdit* (Diu-Kas 25:4) Anazanke huno eri'zama erisia nona'a mizama'a erigahie. (Luk 10:7.)
\p 
\v 19 Elda ne'ku rumo'za kna ami ke huntesaza kea ontahio, hianagi tagufa vahe'mo'o, tare vahe'mo'ma huramagema hanigenka ana nanekea antahio.
\v 20 Hanki kumi'ma nehaza kva vahera, hakare vahe zamufi zamazeri fatgo nehuge'za, maka vahe'mo'za nege'za, kumi' huzankura kore hugahaze.
\v 21 Anumzamofo avufine, Krais Jisasi avufine, huhampri zamante'nea ankero vahe'zmufi kasamuanki, ama nanekea amage' antenka vahera refko osunka, mago zanke hunka zamesi zamanto.
\v 22 Ame'ama hunka kazana mago vahetera antenka mono eri'za erisie hunka azeri o'otio. Mago'a vahe'mo'za kumi' hanafina kagra ana kumipina kagra manigru hunka manio.
\p 
\v 23 Tinkera onenka, osi'a waini tina nenegeno krimpamofona kaza hino, na'ankure hakare zupa krima enerinkure.
\p 
\v 24 Hagi Mago'a vahe'mofo kumi'mo'a amate me'ne, kegaga hunte knare koteno vugahie. Hanki mago'amokizmi kumi'moa frakino me'neankino henka efore hugahie.
\v 25 Anahu kante, hakare vahe'mokizmi knare zamu'zmamo'a amate me'ne. E'ina higeno mago'a vahe'mofo knare zamuzmamo'a oku'a me'neankino, henka'a efore hugahie.
\c 6
\s1 Mono ke hanaza vahe'mo'za amage' ante'snaza naneke
\p 
\v 1 Hagi hakare mono nentahi'za zago e'ori kazokzo eri'za enerimo'za kva vahezamia razampi antahinezamisage'za, nege'za Anumzamofo agi'ane, tagrama knare kema rempima hunezamuna kea huhavizana osugahaze.
\v 2 Iza'o amentintima nehania ne'mo kva'a mani'nesigeno'a, kea ruha'ontagino, na'ankure zamagra neramafuze. Hianagi hakare zupa knare hu'za eriza'zmia eriho, na'ankure e'ima e'nerina eri'zana amentinti nehigeta tavesi'nentona kva ne'mo azahuzana erigahie. Ama'i naneke rempi hunezminka zamasmio.
\p 
\v 3 Hanki mago'a vahe'mo havige naneke nehnigeno, Ranti Jisas Kraisi nanekene, mago'zahu nosnigenka, e'inahu nanekemo'a knare Anumzamofo avu'ava enena trago'otene,
\v 4 agra agu'agesa eri antemrenerino mago'zana antahi ama nosie, hianagi agra mago arimpa osu nanekere agenoka nehuno, nanekegu ke hakare nehigeno, e'i anampinti'ma efore hiana rumofo zanku kesane nehuno, fra nevzino, rimpa oti'oti nehinkeno, vahe'ku huhaviza hunenteno, vahe antahi haviza hunenteno,
\v 5 maka'zupa zamagu'amo knare osu'nea vahe'ene fra nevziza, zamagu zamagesamo haviza hu'nea vahe'mo'za tamage kea nosaze. Zamagrama antahi'zana Anumzamofo nanekefintira feno erisanti haregahune nehaze.
\v 6 Ana hu'neanagi Anumzamofo avu'ava'ma nehu'za agazone hu'za mani'snamo'za, knare zantfa erigahaze.
\v 7 Kasema nerantageta ama mopafina mago'zana erineta ome'none, hagi ama mopama atresuta mago'zana erita ovugahune.
\v 8 Hagi ne'zantine kukenatima me'nenigeta, e'i ana zankura agazone huta nemanita muse hanune.
\v 9 Ana hianagi feno vahe maniku hanaza vahe'mo'za, rezmatagafi evurami'za krifu aheaza hanageno, maka havi avu'avazamofo zamesizampi negi vahe kna nehu'za, zamazeri haviza huzante kezmasane hanageno, ana vahera zamahe haviza huno havi kampi zamavreno uramigahie.
\v 10 Zagogu avesi avesihu avu'avazamo'a maka havi avu'avazamofo agafa'e. Mago'a vahe'mo'za zagogu nehakre'za zamentintia atre'za afete nevazageno, zamasuzamo manizazamifina agonazamo kota zamaheankna nehie.
\p 
\v 11 Hu'neanagi havizampintira atrenka nefrenka, Anumzamofo vahe mani'nananki, fatgo zanke nehunka, Anumzamofo avu'ava nehunka, kamentintia nehunka, vahera kavesi nezmantenka, hanavetinka nevunka fru hunka manio.
\v 12 Kamentintimofo hara knare ha' nehunka, kagima higenka manivava asimu'ma eri'nanana azeri hanavetio, hakare vahe zamufi kagra ko huama hu'nane.
\v 13 Nagra Anumzamofo avufi negasamue, maka'zama asimu ami'nea ne'ene, Krais Jisasi tamage kema Pontias Pailoti avufima huama hu'negu,
\v 14 kagra ana kasegea eri haviza osunka kva hu'negeno, tagri Rantimo Jisas Kraisi efore hino.
\v 15 Agra knama ante'nere fatgo huno egahie, Agrake asomu'ane vugota hu'nea kva ne'ma (sovereign) kinimo'kizmi Kinie, ramokizmi Rane.
\v 16 Agrake'za ofrino manivava hugahie. Tusi'a masa'afi mani'neankiza vahe'mo'za urva'o osugahaze. Mago'mo'e huno onkeneanki'za onkegahaze. Agripina Ra agine, hanave'anena mevava hugahie. Tamage.
\p 
\v 17 Ama mopafi feno vahe mani'naza vahera huzamasmige'za, ana fenozantera zamufa ra osu'za, ana fenozantera zamentinti osiho, hianagi Anumzamofonte zamentintia hiho, Agrama maka'zama tamigeta enerunazanku huta muse hugahune.
\v 18 Zamagrira huzamasmige'za knare'za nehu'za, knare eri'zamo fenozamigna hanige'za, atupama hu'nesaza vahema zamaza hu'zanku nentahi'za, feno zamia retro hiho.
\v 19 E'inama hanu'za, zamagra henka'a esnia knafima erisnaza zamofo agafa'a knare hu'za eri atru nehu'za, ana hu'za azerisaza zanteti tamage mani'zana erigahaze.
\p 
\v 20 Hagi Timotiga, Anumzamo antahi kamino kami'nea eri'zantera kvagri fatgo huo, avufa'a omne'nea nanekegu hafra hugante'nazana, kamefi hunezminka havigema hanaza vahera antahi'ozamio.
\v 21 Ana nehu'za mago'amo'za zamentintia atre'za ru'are vu'naze. Anumzamofo asunku'zamo kagrane mesie. 
